==English==
===Pronunciation===
*[[RP]]: "nyoo͞-zē'lənd, /ˌnjuːˈziːlənd/, /<tt>%nju:"zi:l@nd</tt>/
*(''US''): "n(y)oo͞-zē'lənd, /ˌn(j)uːˈziːlənd/, /<tt>%n(j)u:"zi:l@nd</tt>/

===Etymology===
From Dutch '''[[Nieuw Zeeland]]''', "new Zeeland", after the Dutch settlement in [[Batavia]], which in turn had been named after the Dutch province of [[Zeeland]].

===Proper noun===
'''New Zealand'''

#A country in [[Oceania]], to the east of [[Australia]]. Official name: New Zealand.  Abbreviation: '''NZ'''

